//Chinese Version
玩這個遊戲前，我也接觸過不同AVG，這個是我接觸的唯一談及「死亡」的AVG。雖算不上大作，但卻令我真正反思「面對死亡」。若是你問我，我會推薦所有人都看一看它的故事。這個故事的意義不但在於感人，更在於使我們反思怨天尤人的意義。

//English Version
I've played various AVG before this. This is the only one talking about "Death". Although this is not made by commercial game workshops, but it really touched me and to think of "facing death". If you'd ask me, I'd recommend everyone to dig into the story. The story is not only touching us, but also guiding us thinking of "why should we get anger of our fate?".

To conclude, I absolutely recommend this game.

